{"tid":2415503,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"京深試行數碼人幣 恐增監控隱憂","createTime":"2021-02-20T09:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T10:29:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a96f87f99ad0e066721d255807dd1c83b4e262","tid":2415503,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T09:58:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210219/XXQKPBTHRNCQNGRSBUJMUEKATE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210219%2FXXQKPBTHRNCQNGRSBUJMUEKATE%2F&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkmWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=c62796ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210219%2FXXQKPBTHRNCQNGRSBUJMUEKATE%2F&h=41a08a87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210219/XXQKPBTHRNCQNGRSBUJMUEKATE/</a><br />\n<br />\n京深試行數碼人幣 恐增監控隱憂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/j2sXcbpnRC5lZeUoe1XuTRwgBBA=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RIAWWUPTP5ELXE3I7ODXZ3NWD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fj2sXcbpnRC5lZeUoe1XuTRwgBBA%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRIAWWUPTP5ELXE3I7ODXZ3NWD4.jpg&h=77c316f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n數碼人民幣<br />\n<br />\n北京、深圳、蘇州等地在今個農曆年成為數碼人民幣試點，大派 200元促消費。英國《金融時報》發表分析文章指，數碼人民幣的推出將為國內外帶來更多監控隱憂，相信有助北京控制內地金融科技業，或動搖到支付寶及微信支付現時於內地的壟斷地位。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a1749398ddef65514dfe95b1f4bdd19dacc38fbd","tid":2415503,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:08:23.000Z","msg":"轉錢走喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b2f3be802322ebc0fb0b3b8a370acf312956b8","tid":2415503,"uid":54623,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:10:59.000Z","msg":"無限人民幣大法<br